    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody " xtrc="conbody:1;13:14" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;14:12" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">PET/CT 系统辐射防护需要考虑的放射源主要有三种：</p>
        <ul class="- topic/ul " id="ul_ex4_5qh_bdb" xtrc="ul:1;15:33" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
            <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:1;18:18" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">CT 扫描时 X 射线的辐射</li>
            <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:2;21:18" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">系统校正时使用的放射源的辐射</li>
            <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:3;24:18" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">患者注射放射性核素标记的示踪剂之后，湮灭反应带来的 γ 光子辐射。</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;28:14" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">用户必须请有资质的专业设计公司进行辐射防护设计。在设计时必须根据 CT 球管的工作电流、高压发生器的功率、房间的位置和大小、同位素源和每天患者累计辐射量等因素来计算
            辐射防护的当量。卫生部颁发的相关标准中，对机房的防护有详细的要求，在设计和施工中 必须严格遵行。对于机房混凝土防护墙的厚度、防护门的铅当量、扫描间外面的辐射警示以
            及穿过防护墙的导线导管对防护效果的影响等，都要认真考虑。PET/CT 扫描时，患者需要注射放射性核素标记的示踪剂，示踪剂通常为18F-FDG，按0.1 mCi/kg ~ 0.2
            mCi/kg 的注射剂量计算，同时考虑检查床的最大载重为 250 kg。</p>
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:3;34:14" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">X 射线球管电压分为 70 kV、80 kV、100 kV、120 kV、140 kV 五档。CT 典型扫描运行条件和最大功率扫描条件如下所示。</p>
