        <note class="- topic/note " type="warning" xtrc="note:1;132:30" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:19;133:16" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">过量辐射暴露，人员损伤</p>
            <ul class="- topic/ul " id="ul_ykf_hrh_bdb" xtrc="ul:2;134:37" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:4;135:21" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">房间辐射防护不当可能会对操作人员或其他人员产生伤害，请安装适当的辐射防护。</li>
            </ul>
        </note>
        <note class="- topic/note " type="note" xtrc="note:2;138:27" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:20;139:16" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">客户有责任安装X射线警告指示灯和门机连锁装置</p>
        </note>
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:21;143:14" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">在进行辐射防护设计时，需要同时考虑到对设备的防护和对人员的防护。</p>
        <ul class="- topic/ul " id="ul_nkw_rrh_bdb" xtrc="ul:3;144:33" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
            <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:5;146:171" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:22;147:20" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">设备防护需求</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:23;150:22" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">本系统性能受周围环境的辐射影响，因此，需要考虑外界环境的放射源或放射扫描装置对系统的辐射干扰，尽量将系统所处环境的辐射剂量控制在最低水平。</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:24;153:22" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">需要注意将所有用于质量控制的放射源，置于独立的屏蔽间内。该房间也可以用于储存示踪剂或其他放射性物品，准备水模时也尽量在此房间内进行。</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:6;156:171" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:25;157:20" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">人员防护需求</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:26;160:22" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">系统的人员防电离辐射防护设计以 GB18871《电离辐射防护与辐射安全基本标准》为指导标准。安装场地的屏蔽设计要求应遵守此标准中的 "
                    正常照射的剂量控制应符合剂量限制的规定
                    "，并要遵循辐射防护最优化要求。房间的防电离辐射的效果应最少满足指导标准中的规定限值，即职业照射剂量限值。同时，应遵循国家、地方的相应法律、法规和现行的相关
                    标准。</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:27;166:22" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">所有与 PET/CT 检查的无关人员应处于指定受控区域之外。客户负责安装门机连锁装置，确保只有当 PET/CT 扫描间的防护门关闭时，X
                    射线放射才能启动。</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:28;170:22" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">为避免患者之间互相传递辐射危害，需要设置合理的就诊途径。患者在注射示踪剂之后及扫描过程前后要严格遵照技师的引导，走特定的通道，避免对其他人员，尤其是孕妇和儿童造
                    成危害。</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:29;174:22" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">操作人员需佩戴相关辐射剂量监测仪，对累积辐射剂量进行监控，同时应尽量减少与患者的接触时间，熟练操作，防止不必要的暴露于辐射中。</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <note class="- topic/note " type="warning" xtrc="note:3;177:30" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:30;178:16" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">所有操作人员都需要进行过辐射防护培训</p>
        </note>
        <note class="- topic/note " type="warning" xtrc="note:4;180:30" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:31;181:16" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">射线防护应以当地卫生防疫部门的要求为准，主要取决于工作负荷，设备的位置和周围房屋的用途等。</p>
        </note>
        <note class="- topic/note " type="warning" xtrc="note:5;183:30" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:32;184:16" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Technical_references_for_the_system_operation/Requirements_for_radiation_protection.dita">机房的门窗，墙壁，室顶，地板都要具有相应的防护效果。</p>
        </note>
